{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"d3ef6f8c78","title":"大字报——“农民的生活太苦了”","origin":"《右派言论选辑》（社会主义教育参考资料之一，内部材料　仅供参考，沈阳师范学院社会主义教育办公室 1958．3）","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"d26ec33b1a","index":0,"year":1957,"month":6,"day":null,"articleId":"d3ef6f8c78"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"7eb95ac9a4","name":"沈阳师范学院"},{"id":"aa7714ac45","name":"曾祥基"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"884d02ffb2","type":"title","text":"大字报——“农民的生活太苦了”","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d3ef6f8c78"},{"id":"268152127a","type":"authors","text":"沈阳师范学院曾祥基","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d3ef6f8c78"},{"id":"26ccc2dd6d","type":"subtitle","text":"（曾祥基：沈阳师范学院中文系学生）","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d3ef6f8c78"},{"id":"c919e011c3","type":"paragraph","text":"我是在一个农村中长大的青年，","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d3ef6f8c78"},{"id":"3274a0e22b","type":"paragraph","text":"我知道农民生活的许多苦处。","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d3ef6f8c78"},{"id":"b8639c5c8f","type":"paragraph","text":"我觉得农民的生活真是太苦了，","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d3ef6f8c78"},{"id":"d5295c1884","type":"paragraph","text":"有的地方简直是惨不忍睹。","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d3ef6f8c78"},{"id":"3d10399a14","type":"paragraph","text":"很多农民一日三飡吃的都是稀饭，","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d3ef6f8c78"},{"id":"da0a33dafe","type":"paragraph","text":"很多农民一个月买不到一两猪肉。","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d3ef6f8c78"},{"id":"37922e33db","type":"paragraph","text":"“为什么报纸上还说农民的生活有很大提高，这样的报导怎么能叫人信服？”","index":9,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d3ef6f8c78"}],"page":{"id":"dfc12646f6","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d3ef6f8c78","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_S